                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="family-plan card">
                        <h3>Family Plan Available</h3>
                        <p>Set up protection for your parents or grandparents with our family dashboard.</p>
                        <p>Get alerts about potential risks and manage their security settings.</p>
                        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-outline" style="color: white; border-color: white; margin-top: 1rem;">Learn More</a>
                    </div>
